===Noun===
'''[[brown]] [[dwarf]]''' (''plural'': '''[[brown dwarfs]]''' ''or'' '''[[brown dwarves]]''')
#{{astronomy}}:an [[dwarf star]] that is typically about the size of the planet [[Jupiter]], which has mass approaching that of a star, but insufficient to ignite its elements and cause it to burn as a true star

